728988f-a.folder: Hylan Boulevard & Bedell Avenue, Staten Island, NY
728988f-a.text:
Hylan Boulevard, south side, between Bedell and Page Avenues, showing the south side of the Manee House. The house
is 100 yards south of the Boulevard.
August 27, 1930.
P. L. Sperr
(2)
A view of the west side of the house.
Augst 27, 1930.
P. L. Sperr
